column2: ggplot() + geom_line(aes(x=day, y=number_of_packages, group = num_of_collection_points, color = as.factor(num_of_collection_points))) + ggtitle("Daily Number of Packges - With & Without Collection Points") +labs(y= "Number of Packages", x = "Day n", color = "is Collection Point") + scale_color_manual(labels = c("Without Collection Point", "With One Collection Point"), values = c("#F8766D", "#00BFC4"))
